@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.58
    v1 = (((tmp + 0.70 * tmp + 0.29) * wp.exp(v1 + 0.25)) * (wp.exp(tmp + 0.77) / 0.58))
    v2 = (((v0 + 0.01 + tmp + 0.43) - wp.exp(v0 + 0.28)) / ((v0 + 0.41 - v0 + 0.85) - (v1 + 0.52 * v1 + 0.06)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.80)) * ((tmp + 0.39 + tmp + 0.12) / (tmp + 0.26 + v1 + 0.49)))
    data[tid] = v0
